OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Frain continuing to spread northeast,
OL,7,Fhill snow in north, gales or severe
OL,8,Fgales for a time. Becoming drier and
OL,9,Fclearer overnight with winds easing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FSome bright, sunny spells
OL,12,Ffirst thing. Then cloudier for a time
OL,13,Fwith some showers, wintry on high
OL,14,Fground. Bright spells and showers in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. Blustery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
